
	0 - on-line macro
	a - check contents of ALIAS file
        b - run BF (fancy print) on pointed file
	c - crunch the pointed file
	e - edit the pointed file
	n - invoke NULU on pointed file, filesweep mode
        o - Open a LBR file with VLU
        p - Print a WordStar formatted file with PRINT120
	t - type any file to screen, including crunched files
	u - UNCRunch the pointed file
	v - VTYPE the pointed file
        w - go into Word processing operations


